   <text type="letter">
      <body>
         <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="amh.00013.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
         <opener>
            <salute>Dear Charley,</salute>
         </opener>
         <p>My condition continues favorable&#8212;&amp; if I dared to hope <hi rend="underline">this</hi> will last &amp;
            improve in proportion&#8212;indicates recovery at least, as definitely as any thing
            hitherto&#8212;I think more definitely&#8212;I send you &amp; P.O. order&#8212;which please
            get &amp; pay Godey. Write me a line Thursday or Friday.<ptr target="amh.00013_n1"/></p>

         <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="amh.00013.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/>

      </body>
